content: Claude, this is fantastic, I just think we drastically improved this implementation in about 10 minutes by doing this. What would you say the boost we should expect to receive from this is? And second, I've been working with another Claude chat on this prep, but he's running out of space, we've had a lot of discussion since the last draft of this stuff that led to me prompting you about this. Our relationship is such that we push breakthroughs in thinking with each other at a very rapid pace now. It is really quite fun. Can you give him a very brief update on all this?
